The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Dalmiyas stand

A STAFF REPORTER 

Calcutta: Replying to the oppositions allegation that he was responsible for BCCIs financial sanctions on the CAB, president Jagmohan Dalmiya said on Saturday that hes ready to clarify his stand with them, if required. 

They are welcome to sit with me over this issue? Im ready to discuss it with them and clarify my stand, Dalmiya said. 

He also ruled out the possibility of looking for a substitute to Howrah Unions Nemai Charan Dutta ? who has featured as one of the vice-presidents on both panels of candidates, but expressed his loyalty to the opposition camp on Saturday. 




